{"word":"H6822 - צָפָה - tsâphâh - tsaw-faw' - Behold","slug":"H6822","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָפָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsâphâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-faw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Behold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05E4;&#x05D4; - tsa&#x0302;pha&#x0302;h</b> - <i>tsaw-faw'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>lean</i> forward, that is, to <i>peer</i> into the distance; by implication to <i>observe</i>, <i>await: - </i>behold, espy, look up (well), wait for, (keep the) watch (-man)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4707\">H4707</a>, <a href=\"#/H4708\">H4708</a>, <a href=\"#/H4709\">H4709</a>, <a href=\"#/H6825\">H6825</a>, <a href=\"#/H6827\">H6827</a>, <a href=\"#/H6831\">H6831</a>, <a href=\"#/H6836\">H6836</a>, <a href=\"#/H6837\">H6837</a>, <a href=\"#/H6839\">H6839</a>"}]}